description:
Create src/components/tick-card.ts:

@customElement('tick-card')
export class TickCard extends LitElement {
  @property() tick!: Tick;
  @property({ type: Boolean }) selected = false;
}

Features to port from existing UI:
- Display tick ID, title, type badge
- Priority indicator (color-coded: critical=red, high=peach, medium=yellow, low=green)
- Status badge (open/closed)
- Epic name if has parent
- Blocked indicator if blocked
- Manual task indicator
- Click handler to emit 'tick-selected' event

Styles: Use Shoelace sl-card or custom card with Catppuccin surface colors

Test: Render tick-card with mock tick data, verify all fields display correctly
